title: Soares-Raymond v Nestor-Mladenovic - Wimbledon 2013 MD Final
description:
Wimbledon 2013, Mixed Doubles Final, Soares/Raymond v Nestor/Mladenovic.


Transcoded from SD 576i TS at 2236 Kbps to progressive x264 by ffmpeg with settings -c:v libx264 -crf 23 -preset veryfast -vf "yadif=0:-1:0,hqdn3d=4:4:2:3" -c:a libfdk_aac -b:a 128000 -ac 2.


Four files: warmup (7 mins), match parts 1 and 2, presentation.

There was noticeable chroma noise in the original which I tried to reduce without blurring too much.

The match is split in two at an arbitrary position, so that part 1 could start uploading while part 2 was transcoding.
